text: Almere City FC is a Dutch football club. The club was founded on September 14 2001, which has paid football since 2005. The Almeerse association was part of the Omniworld sports club. Until the 2009/2010 season, the club played under the name FC Omniworld. ==Other websites== *Official website Category:2001 establishments in the Netherlands Category:Dutch football clubs Category:Almere
